    <h2><a href="articles/one-of-my-favorite-mobile-apps-is-mind-wall--it-is-a-simple-puzzle-game-where---">One of my favorite mobile apps is Mind Wall. It is a simple puzzle game where...</a></h2>
    <div class="variables">
    <div class="date">@date=2014-02-24</div>
    <div class="tags">@tags=<a href="tags/games">games</a>, <a href="tags/ld48">ld48</a></div>
    </div>
    <article>
        <p>One of my favorite mobile apps is Mind Wall. It is a simple puzzle game where you need to chip off one square of a wall to fit a tetris like block through the wall. It is mildly challenging, and makes for a good spacial puzzle. It was created for ld48</p>
